<HEADLINE> Fans Battle Heat To See Hill, McGraw  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   JACKSON, Miss. (AP) -- More than 10,000 music fans braved the
stifling heat to hear the husband-and-wife singing team Faith Hill
and Tim McGraw.
</P>
<P>
   McGraw opened the Saturday afternoon show just as the sun broke
free from cloud cover, clad in his signature white T-shirt and
broad-brimmed hat.
</P>
