   Before Hill took the stage at 6:30 p.m., the heat exhaustion
toll had reached double digits.
</P>
<P>
   ''I bought enough water today to pay my water bill,'' joked Joey
Vertucci, 31.
</P>
<P>
   The crowd roared when Hill and McGraw finally took the stage
together for an encore, singing their hit single ''It's Your
Love.''
</P>
