<HEADLINE> Oates Ejected From Rangers-A's Game  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   ARLINGTON, Texas (AP) -- Texas manager Johnny Oates was ejected
from Monday night's game against Oakland after a heated argument
with plate umpire Tony Randazzo.
</P>
<P>
   Oates came onto the field in the fourth inning after Rangers
catcher Ivan Rodriguez had some words with Randazzo, apparently
